{"data":[{"date":"18:07 18/06","title":"Qu\u00e2n b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/quan-bau-duc-du-giai-u17-quoc-gia-2018-voi-thanh-tich-vo-cung-an-tuong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb, HAGL kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 VCK U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>U17 HAGL l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U17 HAGL l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U17 HAGL l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/U17-HAGL.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U17 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u 17/6 v\u1eeba qua, l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i U17 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 6-3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 bao g\u1ed3m: U17 C\u00f4ng An Nh\u00e2n D\u00e2n, Viettel (B\u1ea3ng A); SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An (B\u1ea3ng B); HAGL, Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (B\u1ea3ng C); An Giang (B\u1ea3ng D) v\u00e0 U17 PVF (\u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng cai VCK).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. U17 HAGL l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 26 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 8/10 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ho\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi 37 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb Gia Lai c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi +29 b\u00e0n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 26/06 \u0111\u1ebfn 06/07/2018 t\u1ea1i Trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PVF t\u1ea1i V\u0103n Giang, H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ec5 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m x\u1ebfp l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20/6 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HAGL, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\">HLV HAGL th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn thua SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3697","checkdouble":"188836"},{"date":"21:58 18/06","title":"Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/viet-nam-thai-lan-len-ke-hoach-dang-cai-world-cup-2034.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai VCK World Cup 2034 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra sau \u0111\u00e2y 16 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.</h2><h2>Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, li\u00ean minh M\u1ef9 - Canada \u2013 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2026. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup m\u00e0 FIFA s\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 l\u00ean 48 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f9ng Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f9ng Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/5902-world_cup_eyvd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2034 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb t\u1edd The Straits Times, ba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam A\u0301 g\u1ed3m Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Indonesia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 se\u0303 gia\u0300nh quy\u00ea\u0300n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u1ee6y ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh FIFA, Tengku Abdullah Sultan Ahmad Shah ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o Li\u00ean minh ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (\u0110\u00f4ng Nam A\u0301) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00ea\u0309 hi\u00ea\u0323n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00ec co\u0301 ba \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed1n qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f4\u0300ng h\u01a1\u0323p ta\u0301c nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec M\u1ef9, Mexico v\u00e0 Canada \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 2026.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia trong khu v\u01b0\u0323c n\u00e0y co\u0301 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c c\u01a1 h\u00f4\u0323i. V\u00ea\u0300 khi\u0301a ca\u0323nh na\u0300y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Nam A\u0301 s\u1ebd b\u0103\u0301t ki\u0323p v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. T\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n 16 n\u0103m n\u1eefa v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7\u201d, \u00f4ng Ahmad Shah cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai, c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 nh\u01b0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i li\u00ean minh Vi\u1ec7t \u2013 Th\u00e1i \u2013 Indonesia, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u0103ng cai k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m 2014. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2026.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-viet-nam-co-3-quan-xanh-truoc-them-aff-cup-2018-168-185506.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/dt-viet-nam-co-3-quan-xanh-truoc-them-aff-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-viet-nam-co-3-quan-xanh-truoc-them-aff-cup-2018-168-185506.html\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 3 qu\u00e2n xanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m AFF Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd t\u00ecm 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i thi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 World Cup</span><br>\r\nHLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 World Cup, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n hai v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet-168-188640.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet-168-188640.html\">HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nB\u00ean l\u1ec1 VCK World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Alfred Riedl \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3696","checkdouble":"188859"},{"date":"19:22 18/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/6: Chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU n\u1ed5 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/13/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-186-chi-170-trieu-euro-mu-no-bo-doi-bom-tan-vao-dau-thang-7.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU n\u1ed5 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 186 MU chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro mua 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 186 MU chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro mua 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Gareth Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDaily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Joshua Kimmich n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joshua Kimmich ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Abendzeitung \u0111\u01b0a tin, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00ec... thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng cao \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-se-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-vi-thieu-tham-vong-421-188839.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/dt-anh-se-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-vi-thieu-tham-vong.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-se-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-vi-thieu-tham-vong-421-188839.html\">\u0110T Anh s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00ec... thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nSam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng cao \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Toni Kroos</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Pep nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger ca ng\u1ee3i t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kante, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ca ng\u1ee3i t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 sao Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Porto chi ban Alex Telles voi gia 35 trieu bang\" title=\"Porto ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Alex Telles v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alex Telles</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo A Bola, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-188798.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-188798.html\">Liverpool s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, The Kop ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Meunier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kevin De Bruyne, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi 150 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng Navas mua Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diario Gol cho r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Salah, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Salah.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3695","checkdouble":"188844"},{"date":"04:55 19/06","title":"Hazard: \"Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1eadm m\u1edbi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, ngay t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Eden Hazard c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f2n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ea1i London, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Nh\u1edd Chelsea, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho CLB. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u HLV Conte c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup\" title=\"Hazard vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ng\u00e0y mai, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i n\u1eefa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ng\u1eebng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. \u1ede l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu CLB c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u01a1i, m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa&rdquo; &ndash; Eden Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, trong \u0111\u00f3 Hazard g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0110T n\u00e0o c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn n\u1eefa. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo; &ndash; Eden Hazard k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Bi 3-0 Panama\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Thong-so-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 c\u00f3 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Mertens v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf gi\u00e0nh th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-bi-30-panama-421-188866.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Thong-ke-Bi-vs-Panama---Bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-bi-30-panama-421-188866.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Panama 3-0, b\u1ea3ng G World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3694","checkdouble":"188884"},{"date":"17:49 18/06","title":"K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/8/kem-mieng-u23-viet-nam-bong-da-thai-lan-gap-rut-chuan-bi-cho-asiad.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1eddi gian qua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASI h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASI h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/8/u23-thai-lan-that-bai-ldbd-thai-quyet-tam-cai-cach.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi c\u00e1c \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Malaysia t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tay tr\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i v\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh cho l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23+3 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT) \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 MFF Invitation Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Myanmar.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i MFF Invitation Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y m\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 5/8, quy t\u1ee5 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bao g\u1ed3m ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi U23 Th\u00e1i Lan, U23 Bahrain, ri\u00eang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ed9i U19 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Myanmar c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 17 t\u1ea1i Incheon H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u0103m 2014, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u0169ng '\u00f4ng k\u1eb9' c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c hay Jordan \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV Park Hang Seo cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3693","checkdouble":"188833"},{"date":"14:58 18/06","title":"Fan n\u1eef s\u1ed1 1 Peru l\u00e0m lo\u1ea1n kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i t\u1ea1i Nga","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/fan-nu-so-1-peru-lam-loan-khan-dai-tai-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nissu Cauti t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 fan n\u1eef n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0110T Peru m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i. \u1ede World Cup 2018, Nissu c\u0169ng sang Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&quot;Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u&quot; fan n\u1eef n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng c\u1ee7a Nissu Cauti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 3 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Peru chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i Copa America 2015 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Chile. Nissu v\u1edbi bi\u1ec7t danh &quot;em g\u00e1i&quot; Peru lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u00e1y quay ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u00f4 khi di\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n khoe tr\u1ecdn v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p 3 v\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, Nissu c\u00f2n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ebfu Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Montevideo. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Edinson Cavani \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap Uruguay gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Nissu \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a tr\u00fat b\u1ecf xi\u00eam y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1nh m\u00e0y r\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t phen m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u00f9ng \u0110T Peru, Nissu \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 36 n\u0103m qua &quot;La Rojiblanca&quot; m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc cho Peru v\u00e0 &quot;em g\u00e1i&quot; Nissu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a Nissu - &quot;Bravo, Peru. Bra off, Nissu&quot; (Peru ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o Nissu tr\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng), ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t Peru ch\u01a1i kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/nissu2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3692","checkdouble":"188819"},{"date":"15:04 18/06","title":"H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1n tim fan","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/hanh-dong-dep-cua-ronaldo-lam-don-tim-fan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd trong l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c &quot;ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i tim ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9&quot; v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ecbch thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u0103n.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/photo-1-1529294151523463948852.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc xe bu\u00fdt c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00fac tr\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n, Ronaldo b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu b\u00e9 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang kh\u00f3c r\u01b0ng r\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu b\u00e9 \u0111ang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng b\u1edfi c\u1eadu ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1eddi, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1eeda sau \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 tr\u00e1nh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean an ninh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Ronaldo li\u1ec1n nh\u1ea3y xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfc xe bu\u00fdt r\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi \u00f4m h\u00f4n c\u1eadu b\u00e9. Si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n n\u1edf n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n r\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0a tay lau n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft cho c\u1eadu b\u00e9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 k\u00fd t\u1eb7ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 v\u1ecb fan nh\u00ed \u0111ang m\u1eb7c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u00e2n v\u0103n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu b\u00e9 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: &quot;Th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c r\u1ea5t y\u00eau \u0110TQG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, n\u00f3 \u0111ang kh\u00f3c v\u00ec qu\u00e1 sung s\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng&quot;.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3691","checkdouble":"188821"},{"date":"15:18 18/06","title":"Nhan s\u1eafc n\u00e0ng WAG n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nhan-sac-nang-wag-noi-bat-nhat-tuyen-bi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3690","checkdouble":"188822"},{"date":"15:39 18/06","title":"Hotgirl Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh g\u00e2y b\u00e3o tr\u00ean VTV khi n\u00f3i Pele c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi ... Ronaldo","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/hotgirl-cao-diep-anh-gay-bao-tren-vtv-khi-noi-pele-cung-thoi-voi-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh, m\u1ed9t b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng xinh \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil - Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ee7a VTV \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft khi n\u00f3i xem \u0111\u1ed9i Brazil t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, th\u1eddi c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0... Pele.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng lan truy\u1ec1n m\u1ed9t clip &ldquo;g\u00e2y b\u00e3o&rdquo; khi hotgirl kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham gia ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a VTV &ldquo;ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n&rdquo; kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft&hellip; y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi xem \u0111\u1ed9i Brazil t\u1eeb bao gi\u1edd, b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean: &quot;T\u1eeb khi em c\u00f2n h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5p 1, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, 2002. Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Ronaldinho, Pele ...&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hotgirl Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi n\u00f3i Pele c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hotgirl Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi n\u00f3i Pele c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/1(1).png.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u1ea2nh k\u00e8m n\u1ed9i dung hotgirl trao \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean VTV nhanh ch\u00f3ng lan truy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng. \u1ea2nh: Internet</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a VTV k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0111o\u1ea1n clip c\u00f4 g\u00e1i &ldquo;khoe&rdquo; s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u1edd ngh\u1ec7ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng lan truy\u1ec1n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Facebook.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Pele n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, 2002 v\u1edbi Ronaldo? \u00d4ng \u1ea5y gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1977 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i m\u1eb9 \u1ea1, con l\u1eady m\u1eb9!&rdquo;, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u group Facebook, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 do qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu n\u00ean b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd gay g\u1eaft. C\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 &quot;truy ra&quot; Facebook c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 g\u00e1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh, sinh n\u0103m 1995.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;T\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, em m\u1edbi 5-6 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e3 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Pele \u0111\u00e1 World Cup h\u1ea3?&quot;, m\u1ed9t fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ef1 phi l\u00fd trong l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cao Diep Anh\" title=\"Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/33.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cao Di\u1ec7p Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, VTV \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn World Cup b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c &ldquo;tung&rdquo; h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t hotgirl kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi xinh \u0111\u1eb9p ng\u1ed3i c\u00f9ng b\u00e0n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y l\u00ean s\u00f3ng, nh\u1eefng &ldquo;b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3ng&rdquo; kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a VTV \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp &ldquo;g\u00e2y b\u00e3o&rdquo; do ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd qu\u00e1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, khi l\u00ean s\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i d\u0103m c\u00e2u ba \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ed3i&hellip; c\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft, kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ch\u00ea c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi qu\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo, l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i&rdquo; qu\u1ed1c gia.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i n\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-tunisia-va-du-doan-anh-vs-tunisia-421-188828.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs Tunisia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-sac-nang-wag-noi-bat-nhat-tuyen-bi-o-world-cup-2018-421-188822.html\">Nhan s\u1eafc n\u00e0ng WAG n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-12-nhan-dinh-bang-h-binh-thuong-nhung-kho-luong-421-188818.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 12: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3ng H &ndash; B\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-421-188810.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-421-188808.html\">\u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n: Low \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ebft b\u00e0i?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Ictnews.vn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3689","checkdouble":"188824"},{"date":"13:00 18/06","title":"\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>1. Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m nh\u01b0ng thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp HAGL \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i cho nh\u1eefng ai tr\u00f3t y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 &lsquo;si\u00eau nh\u00e2n&rsquo; v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n Anh, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua, c\u00e1i d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 5-4-1 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Da-Nang-2-1-HAGL-Chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi HAGL. V\u00e0 sang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 2, khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec7nh cho\u1ea1c, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo, H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quen thu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u00f3m n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i BXH. \u0110\u00e3 g\u1ea7n 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00f4i qua, HAGL v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng,&hellip; v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u01a1 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. Y\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e2u h\u00e3y s\u1eeda \u0111\u00f3<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn sau \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL b\u1edbt lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. B\u1ed9 ba trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u, Kim Jin-seo, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed khi\u1ebfn HAGL ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn hai b\u00e0n thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec7 ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Kim Jin-seo. S\u1ef1 v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a HAGL t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kim Jin-seo\" title=\"Kim Jin-seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/hagl-bao-tin-ve-chan-thuong-cua-kim-jinseo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Trung v\u1ec7 Kim Jin-seo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 't\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3' c\u1ee7a HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi 24 b\u00e0n thua. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i V-League trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB HAGL r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho ch\u1eb7ng tourmalet t\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 4 ng\u00e0y/ tr\u1eadn, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t phong \u0111\u1ed9. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 v\u1eadt v\u1edd v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng. C\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, hay V\u0103n Thanh d\u00f9 v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c song nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd mang l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfm tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f3n tay. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng trai \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. Nh\u00ecn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111i b\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0\u1edbc ao hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n &lsquo;l\u01b0\u1eddi di chuy\u1ec3n&rsquo; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. M\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi HAGL. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trung l\u1eadp c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1edfi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SHB Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 b\u1ee9c x\u00fac tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y g\u00e2y \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng &lsquo;ngoan&rsquo; nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ee9c x\u00fac \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HAGL c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u00eau n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch theo c\u00e1ch &lsquo;v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1&rsquo; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd. V\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n, h\u1ecd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c &lsquo;t\u1ec9nh b\u01a1&rsquo; ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea7m d\u1eadp. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u1ea5m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1ch c\u00e2u gi\u1edd th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 14&nbsp;V-League 2018)</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Highlight-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a</span><br>\r\nV\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu thua \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. N\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3688","checkdouble":"188780"},{"date":"15:35 18/06","title":"\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft cho chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/15/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo kh\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">SHB\u00a0\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a trung phong \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/15/toa-sang-truoc-tphcm-sao-shb-da-nang-vi-minh-voi-messi-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed7 Merlo ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 2 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u1ea2nh: Goal.com.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 14 V-League di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean SV\u0110 H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n, TP \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 17/6, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai Pleiku. Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a HAGL v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o cam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo ngay tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n trung v\u1ec7 Kim Jin-seo. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft khi anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ra d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Theo tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e3y s\u00f3ng m\u0169i khi \"\u0103n tr\u1ecdn\" m\u0169i gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Kim Jin-seo trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, Merlo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n Linh b\u00ean ph\u00eda Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng V\u00f5 Huy To\u00e0n. Theo c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u1ef9, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e3n d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Highlight-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eefng t\u1eadt x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\">HLV HAGL th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn thua SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3687","checkdouble":"188823"},{"date":"15:54 18/06","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HAGL, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB HAGL t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 4 tr\u00ean BXH. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat, \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111ang m\u1ea5t d\u1ea7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/15590672_1541363012547079_3004420379754663853_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, HAGL nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh v\u1ea5t \u0111i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang, ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, ph\u1ea7n c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n NHM s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n chung c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qua t\u00e2m th\u01b0 n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng T\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f9ng BHL \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c, t\u00ednh to\u00e1n b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng HAGL h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean v\u0103n chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\"K\u00ednh g\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua,to\u00e0n th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean HAGL 3 mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc, Trung, Nam \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eafng, v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xa h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m km \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i.Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u \u0111ang sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.\u00a0<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n nay, V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i h\u01a1n 1/2 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng HAGL sau g\u1ea7n 4 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0110o\u00e0n Nguy\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f4n l\u1ee9a U19 l\u00ean s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i V League v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 d\u00e0nh cho nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadn l\u1ef1c, h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m,\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra; ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 xin h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u00e8n gi\u0169a, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi trung b\u00ecnh 22, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o n\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t non kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng,nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m \u201cKh\u00f4ng \u00e9p tr\u00e1i ch\u00edn non\u201d m\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, h\u00e0i h\u00f2a theo t\u00e2m sinh l\u00fd.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng, kinh qua ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh, th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb s\u1ebd r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee9c t\u00ednh khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n trong \u1ee9ng x\u1eed, \u00fd ch\u00ed ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n trong tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c...<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f9ng BHL \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c, t\u00ednh to\u00e1n b\u1ed5 sung, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Thay m\u1eb7t to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, xin ng\u00e0n l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5m l\u00f2ng y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 ch\u00ednh C\u00f4ng ty S\u1eefa VPMILK-IQLACPRO \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 trang ph\u1ee5c Mizuno, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Next Media...<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1,c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean th\u1ec3 thao, c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ch\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 </em><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em>World Cup 2018</em></span><em> s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u V-League 2018 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra\".</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl-168-188823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/15/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-tra-gia-dat-cho-chien-thang-nguoc-dong-truoc-hagl-168-188823.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft cho chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n, CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo kh\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\">HLV HAGL th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn thua SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec5m nh\u1eefng t\u1eadt x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3686","checkdouble":"188827"},{"date":"14:47 18/06","title":"Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/man-city-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-sao-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep nh\u1eafm Kroos thay David Silva</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, David Silva l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Toni Kroos v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Toni Kroos v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/man-city-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-sao-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Toni Kroos&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i. Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y anh duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nToni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Real Madrid mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Pep \u1edf Etihad c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u sao Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Jorginho c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Toni Kroos, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/napoli-xac-nhan-man-city-chuan-bi-no-bom-tan-172-188493.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli</span>. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n San Paolo \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Jorginho\" title=\"tien ve Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/napoli-xac-nhan-man-city-chuan-bi-no-bom-tan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Jorginho c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Carlo Ancelotti c\u1ee7a Napoli th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jorginho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Napoli, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Man City \u1edf gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Napoli \u0111\u00f2i t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Man City th\u00ec Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jorginho, HLV Sarri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n The Blues thay Conte, c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3685","checkdouble":"188814"}]}